 />\n三年中困守一崗，雖智不逮，未能盡善，然疲乏之心滿矣，竊或離之，亦不可得，心灰之，此為其二；<br />\n<br />\n勞苦三載，東奔西顧，未曾少安，績或無表，無功亦苦，薪給僵持，無期奈何，是者三。除其而外者，書不盡言，無敘也。<br />\n<br />\n辭不達意，萬望納言。<br />\n<br />\nX部/XXX"},{"pid":"0fccc356531a1fc58c63a9ec7b3a398d7c7cd4ef","tid":1173583,"uid":2666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:33:40.000Z","msg":"Google大把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b820feee7670efc06c8a401a1765fcb3a2a9988a","tid":1173583,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:35:26.000Z","msg":"歸去來兮"},{"pid":"122f9698a21c43798b573965ab7c9b2c68303760","tid":1173583,"uid":112845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:36:06.000Z","msg":"dear boss<br />\n<br />\nI want to drop my gun<br />\n<br />\nyour slave"},{"pid":"32ac585cccc588d40d83089099c23f8201aa7858","tid":1173583,"uid":69125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:36:44.000Z","msg":"you fuck off. I fucking quit. 898"},{"pid":"97f906f995e6635cd65d7261018d92605f7f7b09","tid":1173583,"uid":115042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:37:24.000Z","msg":"Dear Boss<br />\n<br />\nI can't do this all day"},{"pid":"c377d17c014e8b83e20b06759dc40d8953888cfa","tid":1173583,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:38:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2cadf4b06dda6a55ec4214393d33c2afa8d26b9","tid":1173583,"uid":69168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:39:17.000Z","msg":"Dear boss,<br />\nI am inevitable."},{"pid":"525b0360318acbf220d0f029efd7905fa4b369d1","tid":1173583,"uid":168156,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:39:36.000Z","msg":"有冇啲簡單少少，google 搵個啲太複習，細路讀得書少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /